1200w,\n/static/f70b5e15f6ae0e070d32c4978054f95a/98235/evasorganics011.jpg 1800w,\n/static/f70b5e15f6ae0e070d32c4978054f95a/d7d8f/evasorganics011.jpg 2400w,\n/static/f70b5e15f6ae0e070d32c4978054f95a/1ac66/evasorganics011.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Apple juice running out of the press\"\n        title=\"Apple juice running out of the press\"\n        src=\"/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/c35de/evasorganics013.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/afcd2/evasorganics013.jpg 300w,\n/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/82472/evasorganics013.jpg 600w,\n/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/c35de/evasorganics013.jpg 1200w,\n/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/98235/evasorganics013.jpg 1800w,\n/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/d7d8f/evasorganics013.jpg 2400w,\n/static/e73c38c3716739892ef6b2edf3424f00/1ac66/evasorganics013.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"apple juice being bottled\"\n        title=\"apple juice being bottled\"\n        src=\"/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/c35de/evasorganics015.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/afcd2/evasorganics015.jpg 300w,\n/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/82472/evasorganics015.jpg 600w,\n/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/c35de/evasorganics015.jpg 1200w,\n/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/98235/evasorganics015.jpg 1800w,\n/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/d7d8f/evasorganics015.jpg 2400w,\n/static/529f5d5157a8658cfe3ec16b9949d260/1ac66/evasorganics015.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(98%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Bottled apple juice range\"\n        title=\"Bottled apple juice range\"\n        src=\"/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/c35de/evasorganics19.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/afcd2/evasorganics19.jpg 300w,\n/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/82472/evasorganics19.jpg 600w,\n/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/c35de/evasorganics19.jpg 1200w,\n/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/98235/evasorganics19.jpg 1800w,\n/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/d7d8f/evasorganics19.jpg 2400w,\n/static/dd28ead7d768923d101fe56b454f1492/1ac66/evasorganics19.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<p>After the batch has been made I go for a look around the rest of the farm.  As I wander through the farm’s polytunnels I am surrounded by a plenitude of organic veg varieties  – courgette, cucumber, peas, rhubarb, blackberries, raspberries, salad leaves, and much more.  The quality of the fruit and veg looks incredible. This well organised variety of fruit and veg is the outcome of many year’s hard work and the amount of veg grown is tailored to the demands of the veg box scheme. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“A lot of it has been learning through trial and error.  Seeing what works, seeing what doesn’t.  Trying different crops and honing in on what works.  So none of this happened overnight.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Seedlings\"\n        title=\"Seedlings\"\n        src=\"/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/c35de/evasorganics022.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/afcd2/evasorganics022.jpg 300w,\n/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/82472/evasorganics022.jpg 600w,\n/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/c35de/evasorganics022.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/98235/evasorganics022.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/d7d8f/evasorganics022.jpg 2400w,\n/static/6b93d6a45c30c9b8983db2800aa284a7/1ac66/evasorganics022.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Blackberries being picked\"\n        title=\"Blackberries being picked\"\n        src=\"/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/c35de/evasorganics024.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/afcd2/evasorganics024.jpg 300w,\n/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/82472/evasorganics024.jpg 600w,\n/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/c35de/evasorganics024.jpg 1200w,\n/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/98235/evasorganics024.jpg 1800w,\n/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/d7d8f/evasorganics024.jpg 2400w,\n/static/7910584b018a33ea702d871d1355a4ac/1ac66/evasorganics024.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(98%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Polytunnel interior view\"\n        title=\"Polytunnel interior view\"\n        src=\"/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/c35de/evasorganics025.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/afcd2/evasorganics025.jpg 300w,\n/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/82472/evasorganics025.jpg 600w,\n/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/c35de/evasorganics025.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/98235/evasorganics025.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/d7d8f/evasorganics025.jpg 2400w,\n/static/6aa12b79395ad98a35efb670180797cb/1ac66/evasorganics025.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<p>The production of organic fruit and veg doesn’t use any artificial fertilisers or pesticides.  These chemicals can cause damage to the natural world and require the use of fossil fuels in their manufacture.  Here they don’t use any artificial chemicals or heavy machinery, they do everything on a smaller scale and with great concern for the environment.  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“The very nature of growing organically is more balanced and in tune with looking after nature”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(98%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Tomatoes on the vine\"\n        title=\"Tomatoes on the vine\"\n        src=\"/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/c35de/evasorganics028.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/afcd2/evasorganics028.jpg 300w,\n/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/82472/evasorganics028.jpg 600w,\n/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/c35de/evasorganics028.jpg 1200w,\n/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/98235/evasorganics028.jpg 1800w,\n/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/d7d8f/evasorganics028.jpg 2400w,\n/static/cdf20cd06a11e770dfa3fb0e2b8e3e40/1ac66/evasorganics028.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<p>Without the use of such chemicals or heavy machinery, the workload is much more intensive in relation to the yield.  However, the extra cost which consumers pay for organic produce is at the benefit of the planet.</p>\n<p>Robert tells me that this kind of farming that they pursue is a fight back against the type of large scale agriculture that uses artificial chemicals and big machinery burning fossil fuels.  </p>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Picked courgettes\"\n        title=\"Picked courgettes\"\n        src=\"/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/c35de/evasorganics026.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/afcd2/evasorganics026.jpg 300w,\n/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/82472/evasorganics026.jpg 600w,\n/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/c35de/evasorganics026.jpg 1200w,\n/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/98235/evasorganics026.jpg 1800w,\n/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/d7d8f/evasorganics026.jpg 2400w,\n/static/4d607be7e22691f36e0af64a51578083/1ac66/evasorganics026.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Raspberry\"\n        title=\"Raspberry\"\n        src=\"/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/c35de/evasorganics031.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/afcd2/evasorganics031.jpg 300w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/82472/evasorganics031.jpg 600w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/c35de/evasorganics031.jpg 1200w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/98235/evasorganics031.jpg 1800w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/d7d8f/evasorganics031.jpg 2400w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/1ac66/evasorganics031.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<figure class=\"markdown-grid\"><div class=\"markdown-grid-grid\" style=\"\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(48%, 1fr));\n          \">\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Cucumber\"\n        title=\"Cucumber\"\n        src=\"/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/c35de/evasorganics037.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/afcd2/evasorganics037.jpg 300w,\n/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/82472/evasorganics037.jpg 600w,\n/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/c35de/evasorganics037.jpg 1200w,\n/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/98235/evasorganics037.jpg 1800w,\n/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/d7d8f/evasorganics037.jpg 2400w,\n/static/e92b4b915f616a4fe79937b90175b972/1ac66/evasorganics037.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Polytunnel view\"\n        title=\"Polytunnel view\"\n        src=\"/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/c35de/evasorganics35.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/afcd2/evasorganics35.jpg 300w,\n/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/82472/evasorganics35.jpg 600w,\n/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/c35de/evasorganics35.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/98235/evasorganics35.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/d7d8f/evasorganics35.jpg 2400w,\n/static/6b107dbf8a750efc01001bade9a3e012/1ac66/evasorganics35.jpg 3000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n</div></figure>\n<p>When questioned about the momentum behind the organic movement, Robert strongly believes that there is not enough focus surrounding it in the media.  Despite consumers beginning to have more concerns about plastic usage and the environmental cost of food transportation, organic farming still doesn’t get mentioned much despite being the most obvious way of growing food sustainably.</p>\n<p>The entire site is 16 acres but they currently only use about a third of this.  There are plans for a new orchard in their largest field, which they’re keen on creating as an agroforestry project.  This means they would have a mixture of elements among the rows of apple trees; such as hedgerows, rhubarb &#x26; a wildlife pond.  The system would help maintain a healthy soil and provide areas for wildlife to flourish.  Robert emphasises how such a project would also aid the environment through carbon sequestration – the removal and storage of carbon from the atmosphere into the soil through biological processes such as photosynthesis.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“At the same time you’re thinking about nature.  So you’ve got the planting of hedgerows, establishing wildlife patches and a wildlife pond”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>In further response to their concerns for the environment, Eva’s Organics has intentions to work towards becoming self-sufficient with their electricity and water supply.  As part of the agroforestry project they intend to install an array of solar panels to meet their electricity requirements.  A rain water collection system and a natural spring are already in use, both of which they use to irrigate the polytunnels.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“We want to be able to create food and nice sustainable products without impacting on the planet in a detrimental way, which I think is often overlooked.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>At a time where the evidence of man-made damage to the environment is so prolific, it is important for both consumers and producers to be aware of how they’re affecting the environment.  Eva’s Organics is a great example of a company which seems to be based around these environmental ethics whilst providing great quality produce to the local area.</p>\n<p>You can find out more about organic farming on the <a href=\"https://www.soilassociation.org/organic-living/organic-farming/\">Soil Association website</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Eva's Organics","date":"July 21, 2019","slug":"/evasorganics","location":"Cumbria","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/81ef8/evasorganics031.jpg","srcSet":"/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/c83a6/evasorganics031.jpg 300w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/775d9/evasorganics031.jpg 600w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/81ef8/evasorganics031.jpg 1200w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/fb184/evasorganics031.jpg 1800w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/c82f6/evasorganics031.jpg 2400w,\n/static/41bb721c63815631a0811e283f13e3e6/7146c/evasorganics031.jpg 3000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/evasorganics"}}}